{"about_the_game":"Reviews by curators<br><br><strong>Gaming Grandma</strong><br><i>&quot;RAZE 2070-very nice sci-fi game of the future, in which we will shoot with robots with different weapons, in different locations with cool graphics. The game is beautiful thanks to the new engine, I recommend it.&quot;</i><br><br><strong>~Universal Gamers~</strong><br><i>&quot;An incredibly challenging first-person shooter where the goal is to survive an attack of murderous robots. Good gameplay mechanics based on Unreal Engine 4. Must try!&quot;</i><br><br><br>Embark on a thrilling science fiction adventure with RAZE 2070. Immerse yourself in stunning graphics that bring the game to life as you navigate a futuristic world where survival is paramount, no matter the cost.<br><br><strong>THE STORY: </strong>.<br>As the space for humanity on Earth diminishes, new frontiers had to be sought in the depths of space. However, this pursuit sparked conflicts and minor wars. In an attempt to overcome these challenges, humans turned to genetic fusion with robots. Yet, this controversial development caused a deep division, ultimately leading to the outbreak of the first Great War.<br><br><strong>And you're right in the middle. </strong><br><br>The impurity of blood gives rise to the rise of the Helragna cult. They are dedicated to fighting on even in death and seizing world dominance. Their ultimate goal is to purge humanity entirely, allowing only the strong and pure-blooded to survive. To achieve this, the Helragnas embark on the transformation of fallen souls into Draugbots. By employing runes and magical rituals, the souls of fallen soldiers are ensnared and infused into robotic entities, giving rise to the creation of Draugbots.<br><br><strong>Grab your Gear</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564230/extras/chest.gif?t=1687090546\" /><br><br>The deceased soldiers gain enhanced strength through their mechanized shells, never succumbing to expiration! The primary purpose of Draugbots is to eliminate anyone deemed unworthy, leaving only the pure ones to ascend to Vallhala.<br><br><strong>Destroy all your enemys! </strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564230/extras/kill.gif?t=1687090546\" /><br><br><br>And so, the Helragnas' tide turns.<br>Take on the role of Sergeant Aleksi Soldier and join the battle against the relentless Draugbots. As a vital member of the &quot;Defender of The Free World&quot; (DFW), the destiny of humanity rests squarely in your hands. Your mission is clear: stand against the relentless waves of enemy assaults and survive at all costs.<br><br><strong>MAIN FEATURES: </strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Action-packed gameplay. </strong><br>     Grab your weapons and dismember your enemies!<br><br></li><li><strong>Survive</strong>.<br>     Your mission is to survive as long as possible! Wave after wave!<br><br></li><li><strong>No mercy. </strong><br>     Your enemies will show you no mercy!<br><br></li><li> <strong>Success. </strong><br>     Achieve a variety of done!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"GAME OVER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1564230/99f518294be6c65ddbd1e14b577a11ccb802e7d5.jpg"},{"name":"You shall not pass","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1564230/d81bb6f674a5834d22bf30d9cbe68f3bcedc9c17.jpg"},{"name":"First blood \u00e4hh oil","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1564230/222248c4042c6441f44fe666ca0bc6c76e0e03d8.jpg"},{"name":"PEW PEW","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1564230/830c8e96973da2bdb0bb90d1adb44120de3127d3.jpg"},{"name":"Give me some stuff","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1564230/4f53b4cfc5becc283342957faee9ef82256d8a9